## 2. Strings

| Concept | Java | Node.js | Python |
|---|---|---|---|
| Interpolation | `String.format("Hi %s", name)` | `` `Hi ${name}` `` | `f"Hi {name}"` |
| Length | `str.length()` | `str.length` | `len(str)` |
| Substring | `str.substring(0, 4)` | `str.slice(0, 4)` | `str[0:4]` |
| Split | `str.split(",")` | `str.split(",")` | `str.split(",")` |
| Join | `String.join(",", list)` | `arr.join(",")` | `",".join(list)` |
| Trim | `str.trim()` | `str.trim()` | `str.strip()` |
| Upper/Lower | `str.toUpperCase()` | `str.toUpperCase()` | `str.upper()` |
| Contains | `str.contains("x")` | `str.includes("x")` | `"x" in str` |
| Replace | `str.replace("a","b")` | `str.replace("a","b")` | `str.replace("a","b")` |
| Multiline | `""" text block """` (Java 15+) | `` `backtick` `` | `"""triple"""` |

### 🧪 Practice
```java
// Java
String name = "Mani";
int age = 30;
String msg = String.format("I am %s, %d yrs old", name, age);
String s = "Software";
System.out.println(s.substring(0, 4)); // "Soft"
String csv = "Mani,Kumar,Kathi";
String[] parts = csv.split(",");
System.out.println(String.join(" | ", parts)); // Mani | Kumar | Kathi
```
```javascript
// Node.js
const name = "Mani", age = 30;
const msg = `I am ${name}, ${age} yrs old`;
let s = "Software";
console.log(s.slice(0, 4)); // "Soft"
let csv = "Mani,Kumar,Kathi";
let parts = csv.split(",");
console.log(parts.join(" | ")); // Mani | Kumar | Kathi
```
```python
# Python
name, age = "Mani", 30
msg = f"I am {name}, {age} yrs old"
s = "Software"
print(s[0:4])  # "Soft"
csv = "Mani,Kumar,Kathi"
parts = csv.split(",")
print(" | ".join(parts))  # Mani | Kumar | Kathi
```

