## 4. Loops

| Concept | Java | Node.js | Python |
|---|---|---|---|
| For | `for (int i=0; i<5; i++)` | `for (let i=0; i<5; i++)` | `for i in range(5):` |
| For Each | `for (String s : list)` | `for (const s of arr)` | `for s in list:` |
| While | `while (x > 0) {}` | `while (x > 0) {}` | `while x > 0:` |
