while (n <= 5) { System.out.println(n); n++; }
```
```javascript
// Node.js
// For
for (let i = 0; i < 5; i++) console.log(i);

// For Each
const langs = ["Java", "Node", "Python"];
for (const l of langs) console.log(l);

// While
