## 13. Quick Mental Model

| | Java | Node.js | Python |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Best For** | Enterprise backends, Android, high-perf systems | APIs, real-time, microservices, CLI | ML/AI, data science, scripting, automation |
| **Strength** | Type safety, JVM, Spring Boot, multithreading | Non-blocking I/O, npm ecosystem, async-first | Readability, libraries (NumPy, Pandas, TF) |
| **Watch Out** | Verbosity, boilerplate, slow startup | Callback hell, weak typing, single-threaded | GIL limits threads, slower raw speed |
| **Runs On** | JVM (platform independent) | V8 engine (Chrome/Node) | CPython interpreter |
| **Typing** | Static, strong | Dynamic, weak | Dynamic, strong |

